##DESCRIPTION
##  Find the slope of a tangent line by evaluating the limit definition of the derivative
##ENDDESCRIPTION

##Tagged by ynw2d

## DBsubject(Calculus - single variable)
## DBchapter(Limits and continuity)
## DBsection(Applications - tangent lines and slopes)
## Date(6/3/2002)
